        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and finely dice your <strong>brown onion[s]</strong></p><p>Combine your <strong>pork mince</strong> (remove the paper if required!) and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>diced onion </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) in a bowl with a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up until thoroughly combined (clean hands is the best way!)</p><p>Divide and shape them into 5 meatballs per person – these are your <strong>pork meatballs</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1702388110137-x200.jpg",
