        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid)) over a medium-high heat with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong></p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>pork meatballs</strong> to the pan and cook for 2 min on each side or until browned</p><p>Once the meatballs have browned, transfer them to a plate and set aside, reserving the pan</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
