            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the reserved pan to a medium heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>remaining diced onion </strong>with a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 4-5 min or until beginning to soften</p><p>Dissolve your <strong>chicken stock mix</strong>, <strong>Henderson's Relish </strong>and <strong>Dijon mustard</strong> in 300ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[390ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[550ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
