          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion has softened, add 1 tbsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp]</span> <strong>flour </strong>to the pan and cook for 1 min</p><p>Gradually whisk in the <strong>chicken stock </strong>and cook for 2-3 min until slightly thickened</p>",
      "order": 6,
