      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the sauce has thickened, return the <strong>browned meatballs</strong> to the pan and cook, covered, for 12-15<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span>min further or until the meatballs are cooked through (no pink meat!) – these are your <strong>Swedish-style meatballs & gravy</strong></p>",
