    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Swedish-style meatballs & gravy</strong> with the <strong>cranberry brown rice</strong> and <strong>dill quick-pickled cucumber </strong>to the side</p><p>Pour any <strong>remaining gravy</strong> over the meatballs and add a dollop of <strong>cranberry sauce</strong> on top</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>remaining chopped dill</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
